South Africa’s biggest and best tech website MyBroadband hosted its Digital Marketing Conference on 18 April. The conference offered marketing professionals insight into the latest digital marketing trends and provided a platform for delegates to interact and network with South Africa’s top industry experts. Delegates also enjoyed presentations from industry experts, covering topics like native marketing, display advertising, email marketing, social media marketing, sponsored content, and more. Speakers included Clockwork Media MD Tom Manners, Everlytic Brand Manager Karyn Strybos, Brand communication specialist Musa Kalenga, 10and5 and 5Tudio MD Uno De Waal, Shift One Advertising Agency CEO Dylan Kohlstädt, and MyBroadband’s Rudolph Muller and Kevin Lancaster. For more information, visit the MyBroadband Digital Marketing Conference website.                  